    "parse": {
      "title": "Quarry",
      "pageid": 1792,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"floatright\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120947\">.mw-parser-output .mapcontainer{position:relative;overflow:hidden}.mw-parser-output .maplocation{position:absolute}</style><div class=\"mapcontainer\" style=\"width:400px;height:244px;\"><div class=\"maplocation\" style=\"left:324px;top:43px;\"><img alt=\"Maplocation.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/20px-Maplocation.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/30px-Maplocation.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5c/Maplocation.png/40px-Maplocation.png 2x\" /></div><img alt=\"Map.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/4/43/Map.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"244\" /></div></div>\n<dl><dd><i>This article is about the <a href=\"/Pelican_Town\" title=\"Pelican Town\">Pelican Town</a> quarry. For <a href=\"/Ginger_Island\" title=\"Ginger Island\">Ginger Island</a>, see <a href=\"/Ginger_Island#Dig_Site\" title=\"Ginger Island\">Ginger Island#Dig Site</a>.</i></dd></dl>\n<p>The <b>Quarry</b> consists of a large area with a wide selection of rocks and <a href=\"/Mining#Mining_Nodes\" title=\"Mining\">mining nodes</a> that are randomly generated.  Each day there is a chance that new rocks and nodes as well as <a href=\"/Trees\" title=\"Trees\">oak and maple tree</a> seeds will be generated.  It is part of the same map as <a href=\"/The_Mountain\" title=\"The Mountain\">the Mountain</a>, therefore it has the same <a href=\"/Foraging#Foraged_Items\" title=\"Foraging\">forageable</a> items and <a href=\"/Artifact_Spot\" title=\"Artifact Spot\">Artifact Spot</a> contents as the Mountain.\n</p><p>The Quarry is unlocked by completing the <a href=\"/Bundles#Crafts_Room\" title=\"Bundles\">Crafts Room bundles</a> in the <a href=\"/Community_Center\" title=\"Community Center\">Community Center</a> or by purchasing \"Bridge\" from the <a href=\"/Joja_Community_Development_Form\" title=\"Joja Community Development Form\">Joja Community Development Form</a> for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"25000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />25,000g</span>. \n</p><p>The Quarry itself can be home to every ore and gem in the game. However, stones containing valuable items like <a href=\"/Iridium_Ore\" title=\"Iridium Ore\">Iridium Ore</a> or <a href=\"/Prismatic_Shard\" title=\"Prismatic Shard\">Prismatic Shards</a> are much rarer and the player may have to wait several seasons for new ones to spawn.\n</p><p>The Entrance to the <a href=\"/Quarry_Mine\" title=\"Quarry Mine\">Quarry Mine</a> is on the western side of the quarry, above the bridge.  The <a href=\"/Minecart\" title=\"Minecart\">Minecart</a> can also take the player to the Quarry once the bridge is repaired. (The Minecart is unlocked by either completing the <a href=\"/Bundles#Boiler_Room\" title=\"Bundles\">Boiler Room bundles</a> or by purchasing \"Minecarts\" from the <a href=\"/Joja_Community_Development_Form\" title=\"Joja Community Development Form\">Joja Community Development Form</a> at <a href=\"/JojaMart\" title=\"JojaMart\">JojaMart</a> for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"15000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />15,000g</span>.)\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Spawning\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Spawning</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Usable_Space\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Usable Space</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Gallery\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gallery</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Spawning\">Spawning</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Quarry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Spawning\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Each day new rocks, nodes, oak and maple seeds will spawn. In year 1, the game attempts to add 7 things from the table below. This increases by 2 each year up to a maximum of 16. Existing rocks block new spawns, so it is wise to keep the quarry entirely cleared.<sup id=\"cite_ref-spawns_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-spawns-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Rock Type\n</th>\n<th>Chance\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Stone_Index32.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stone Index32.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/fb/Stone_Index32.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a><a href=\"/File:Stone_Index38.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stone Index38.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/70/Stone_Index38.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a><a href=\"/File:Stone_Index40.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stone Index40.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/f1/Stone_Index40.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a><a href=\"/File:Stone_Index42.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stone Index42.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/3a/Stone_Index42.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> Rock\n</td>\n<td>45.1%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Stone_Index668.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stone Index668.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/4/45/Stone_Index668.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a><a href=\"/File:Stone_Index670.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stone Index670.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/2/25/Stone_Index670.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> Rock which can drop coal\n</td>\n<td>22.6%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Copper_Node.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Copper Node.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/c8/Copper_Node.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Copper_Ore\" title=\"Copper Ore\">Copper</a> Node\n</td>\n<td>7.99%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Coal_Node_Quarry_01.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Coal Node Quarry 01.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/3b/Coal_Node_Quarry_01.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a><a href=\"/File:Coal_Node_Quarry_02.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Coal Node Quarry 02.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d6/Coal_Node_Quarry_02.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Coal\" title=\"Coal\">Coal</a> Node\n</td>\n<td>7.52%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Oak_Stage_2.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Oak Stage 2.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/9/94/Oak_Stage_2.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a><a href=\"/File:Maple_Stage_2.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Maple Stage 2.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7b/Maple_Stage_2.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Oak_Tree\" title=\"Oak Tree\">Oak</a> or <a href=\"/Maple_Tree\" title=\"Maple Tree\">Maple</a> Tree\n</td>\n<td>6%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Iron_Node.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Iron Node.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/ea/Iron_Node.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Iron_Ore\" title=\"Iron Ore\">Iron</a> Node\n</td>\n<td>3.94%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Artifact_tile.gif\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Artifact tile.gif\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/41/Artifact_tile.gif/48px-Artifact_tile.gif\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"37\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/41/Artifact_tile.gif/72px-Artifact_tile.gif 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/4/41/Artifact_tile.gif/96px-Artifact_tile.gif 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/Artifact_Spot\" title=\"Artifact Spot\">Artifact Spot</a>\n</td>\n<td>3.13%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Gold_Node.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Gold Node.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/8/88/Gold_Node.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Gold_Ore\" title=\"Gold Ore\">Gold</a> Node\n</td>\n<td>1.33%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Seed_Spot.gif\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Seed Spot.gif\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7b/Seed_Spot.gif\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Seed_Spot\" title=\"Seed Spot\">Seed Spot</a>\n</td>\n<td>0.553%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Diamond_Node.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Diamond Node.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0e/Diamond_Node.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Diamond\" title=\"Diamond\">Diamond</a> Node\n</td>\n<td>0.242%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Ruby_Node.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Ruby Node.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e8/Ruby_Node.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Ruby\" title=\"Ruby\">Ruby</a> Node\n</td>\n<td>0.242%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Jade_Node.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Jade Node.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/9/97/Jade_Node.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Jade\" title=\"Jade\">Jade</a> Node\n</td>\n<td>0.242%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Amethyst_Node.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Amethyst Node.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/8/8f/Amethyst_Node.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Amethyst\" title=\"Amethyst\">Amethyst</a> Node\n</td>\n<td>0.242%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Topaz_Node.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Topaz Node.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/3f/Topaz_Node.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Topaz\" title=\"Topaz\">Topaz</a> Node\n</td>\n<td>0.242%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Emerald_Node.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Emerald Node.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/c0/Emerald_Node.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Emerald\" title=\"Emerald\">Emerald</a> Node\n</td>\n<td>0.242%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Aquamarine_Node.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Aquamarine Node.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0a/Aquamarine_Node.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Aquamarine\" title=\"Aquamarine\">Aquamarine</a> Node\n</td>\n<td>0.242%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Mystic_Stone.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Mystic Stone.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/4/4b/Mystic_Stone.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Mining#Mystic_Stone\" title=\"Mining\">Mystic Stone</a>\n</td>\n<td>0.188%\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Iridium_Node.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Iridium Node.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/4/4d/Iridium_Node.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> <a href=\"/Iridium_Ore\" title=\"Iridium Ore\">Iridium</a> Node\n</td>\n<td>0.0133%\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usable_Space\">Usable Space</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Quarry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Usable Space\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Quarry_tiles.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Quarry tiles.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/29/Quarry_tiles.png/300px-Quarry_tiles.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"276\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/29/Quarry_tiles.png/450px-Quarry_tiles.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/29/Quarry_tiles.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Quarry_tiles.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div></div></div></div>\n<p>This image shows the usable space in the Quarry. Colored tiles (yellow or blue) can be used to place <a href=\"/Crafting#Decor\" title=\"Crafting\">paths</a>, <a href=\"/Crafting#Artisan_Equipment\" title=\"Crafting\">artisan equipment</a> and <a href=\"/Crafting#Refining_Equipment\" title=\"Crafting\">refining equipment</a>. Yellow tiles (tillables) may also be used to plant <a href=\"/Trees\" title=\"Trees\">common trees</a>.\n</p><p><a href=\"/Villagers\" title=\"Villagers\">Villagers</a> do not travel through the Quarry or on its bridge, so items placed there are safe from destruction.\n</p>\n<div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\">Gallery</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Quarry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Gallery\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/File:Quarry.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/28/Quarry.png/104px-Quarry.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"104\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/28/Quarry.png/156px-Quarry.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/2/28/Quarry.png/207px-Quarry.png 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>The Quarry in Spring\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/File:Mystic_Stone.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/4/4b/Mystic_Stone.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>A Mystic Stone found in the Quarry\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/File:Iridum_ore_mined.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/0f/Iridum_ore_mined.png/115px-Iridum_ore_mined.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"115\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/0f/Iridum_ore_mined.png/172px-Iridum_ore_mined.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/0/0f/Iridum_ore_mined.png/230px-Iridum_ore_mined.png 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>Upon mining a Mystic Stone\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Quarry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-spawns-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-spawns_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">See <samp>Mountain::quarryDayUpdate</samp> in the game code.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Quarry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Bombs no longer cause ore nodes to drop stone. Bombs now destroy gem nodes. The Quarry now spawns oak and maple trees. Added the <a href=\"/Quarry_Mine\" title=\"Quarry Mine\">Quarry Mineshaft</a> to the Quarry.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: <a href=\"/Mining#Coal_Node\" title=\"Mining\">Coal Nodes</a> can now appear in the Quarry. Quarry production now increases yearly.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Locations\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Locations\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Backwoods\" title=\"Backwoods\">Backwoods</a> • <a href=\"/The_Beach\" title=\"The Beach\">Beach</a> • <a href=\"/Bus_Stop\" title=\"Bus Stop\">Bus Stop</a> • <a href=\"/The_Desert\" title=\"The Desert\">Calico Desert</a> • <a href=\"/Cindersap_Forest\" title=\"Cindersap Forest\">Cindersap Forest</a> • <a href=\"/The_Farm\" title=\"The Farm\">Farm</a> • <a href=\"/The_Cave\" title=\"The Cave\">Farm Cave</a> • <a href=\"/Farm_Pond\" title=\"Farm Pond\">Farm Pond</a> •  <a href=\"/Graveyard\" title=\"Graveyard\">Graveyard</a> • <a href=\"/Ginger_Island\" title=\"Ginger Island\">Ginger Island</a> • <a href=\"/Mastery_Cave\" title=\"Mastery Cave\">Mastery Cave</a> • <a href=\"/Minecart\" title=\"Minecart\">Minecart</a> • <a href=\"/The_Mines\" title=\"The Mines\">Mines</a> • <a href=\"/The_Mountain\" title=\"The Mountain\">Mountain</a> • <a href=\"/Mutant_Bug_Lair\" title=\"Mutant Bug Lair\">Mutant Bug Lair</a> • <a href=\"/Pelican_Town\" title=\"Pelican Town\">Pelican Town</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Quarry</a> • <a href=\"/Quarry_Mine\" title=\"Quarry Mine\">Quarry Mine</a> • <a href=\"/Railroad\" title=\"Railroad\">Railroad</a> • <a href=\"/Secret_Woods\" title=\"Secret Woods\">Secret Woods</a> • <a href=\"/The_Sewers\" title=\"The Sewers\">Sewers</a> • <a href=\"/Skull_Cavern\" title=\"Skull Cavern\">Skull Cavern</a> • <a href=\"/The_Summit\" title=\"The Summit\">Summit</a> • <a href=\"/The_Tunnel\" title=\"The Tunnel\">Tunnel</a> • <a href=\"/Volcano_Dungeon\" title=\"Volcano Dungeon\">Volcano Dungeon</a> • <a href=\"/Witch%27s_Swamp\" title=\"Witch&#39;s Swamp\">Witch's Swamp</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414134340\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.063 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.071 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 308/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2323/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 438/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2180/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   30.035      1 -total\n 33.38%   10.027      1 Template:Map\n 11.14%    3.345      2 Template:History\n  8.51%    2.556      2 Template:Price\n  6.77%    2.033      2 Template:Version\n  5.55%    1.666      1 Template:For\n  4.77%    1.432      1 Template:Clear\n  4.05%    1.216      1 Template:NavboxLocations\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:1792-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414134340 and revision id 182011\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "<div class=\"floatright\">{{map|324|43}}</div>\n{{For|[[Ginger Island]]|Ginger Island#Dig Site|R=This article is about the [[Pelican Town]] quarry.}}\nThe '''Quarry''' consists of a large area with a wide selection of rocks and [[Mining#Mining Nodes|mining nodes]] that are randomly generated.  Each day there is a chance that new rocks and nodes as well as [[Trees|oak and maple tree]] seeds will be generated.  It is part of the same map as [[the Mountain]], therefore it has the same [[Foraging#Foraged Items|forageable]] items and [[Artifact Spot]] contents as the Mountain.\n\nThe Quarry is unlocked by completing the [[Bundles#Crafts Room|Crafts Room bundles]] in the [[Community Center]] or by purchasing \"Bridge\" from the [[Joja Community Development Form]] for {{Price|25000}}. \n\nThe Quarry itself can be home to every ore and gem in the game. However, stones containing valuable items like [[Iridium Ore]] or [[Prismatic Shard]]s are much rarer and the player may have to wait several seasons for new ones to spawn.\n\nThe Entrance to the [[Quarry Mine]] is on the western side of the quarry, above the bridge.  The [[Minecart]] can also take the player to the Quarry once the bridge is repaired. (The Minecart is unlocked by either completing the [[Bundles#Boiler Room|Boiler Room bundles]] or by purchasing \"Minecarts\" from the [[Joja Community Development Form]] at [[JojaMart]] for {{Price|15000}}.)\n\n==Spawning==\nEach day new rocks, nodes, oak and maple seeds will spawn. In year 1, the game attempts to add 7 things from the table below. This increases by 2 each year up to a maximum of 16. Existing rocks block new spawns, so it is wise to keep the quarry entirely cleared.<ref name=\"spawns\" />\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Rock Type\n!Chance\n|-\n|[[File:Stone Index32.png]][[File:Stone Index38.png]][[File:Stone Index40.png]][[File:Stone Index42.png]] Rock\n|45.1%\n|-\n|[[File:Stone Index668.png]][[File:Stone Index670.png]] Rock which can drop coal\n|22.6%\n|-\n|[[File:Copper Node.png]] [[Copper Ore|Copper]] Node\n|7.99%\n|-\n|[[File:Coal Node Quarry 01.png]][[File:Coal Node Quarry 02.png]] [[Coal]] Node\n|7.52%\n|-\n|[[File:Oak Stage 2.png]][[File:Maple Stage 2.png]] [[Oak Tree|Oak]] or [[Maple Tree|Maple]] Tree\n|6%\n|-\n|[[File:Iron Node.png]] [[Iron Ore|Iron]] Node\n|3.94%\n|-\n|[[File:Artifact tile.gif|48px]] [[Artifact Spot]]\n|3.13%\n|-\n|[[File:Gold Node.png]] [[Gold Ore|Gold]] Node\n|1.33%\n|-\n|[[File:Seed Spot.gif]] [[Seed Spot]]\n|0.553%\n|-\n|[[File:Diamond Node.png]] [[Diamond]] Node\n|0.242%\n|-\n|[[File:Ruby Node.png]] [[Ruby]] Node\n|0.242%\n|-\n|[[File:Jade Node.png]] [[Jade]] Node\n|0.242%\n|-\n|[[File:Amethyst Node.png]] [[Amethyst]] Node\n|0.242%\n|-\n|[[File:Topaz Node.png]] [[Topaz]] Node\n|0.242%\n|-\n|[[File:Emerald Node.png]] [[Emerald]] Node\n|0.242%\n|-\n|[[File:Aquamarine Node.png]] [[Aquamarine]] Node\n|0.242%\n|-\n|[[File:Mystic Stone.png]] [[Mining#Mystic Stone|Mystic Stone]]\n|0.188%\n|-\n|[[File:Iridium Node.png]] [[Iridium Ore|Iridium]] Node\n|0.0133%\n|}\n\n==Usable Space==\n[[File:Quarry tiles.png|thumb|right|300px]]\nThis image shows the usable space in the Quarry. Colored tiles (yellow or blue) can be used to place [[Crafting#Decor|paths]], [[Crafting#Artisan Equipment|artisan equipment]] and [[Crafting#Refining Equipment|refining equipment]]. Yellow tiles (tillables) may also be used to plant [[Trees|common trees]].\n\n[[Villagers]] do not travel through the Quarry or on its bridge, so items placed there are safe from destruction.\n{{clear}}\n\n==Gallery==\n<gallery>\nQuarry.png|The Quarry in Spring\nMystic Stone.png|A Mystic Stone found in the Quarry\nIridum ore mined.png|Upon mining a Mystic Stone\n</gallery>\n\n==References==\n<references>\n<ref name=\"spawns\">See <samp>Mountain::quarryDayUpdate</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.4|Bombs no longer cause ore nodes to drop stone. Bombs now destroy gem nodes. The Quarry now spawns oak and maple trees. Added the [[Quarry Mine|Quarry Mineshaft]] to the Quarry.}}\n{{History|1.6|[[Mining#Coal Node|Coal Nodes]] can now appear in the Quarry. Quarry production now increases yearly.}}\n\n{{NavboxLocations}}\n\n[[Category:Mountain Locations]]\n\n[[de:Steinbruch]]\n[[es:Cantera]]\n[[fr:Carrière]]\n[[it:Cava]]\n[[ja:石切場]]\n[[ko:채석장]]\n[[hu:Kőfejtő]]\n[[pt:Pedreira]]\n[[ru:Карьер]]\n[[tr:Taş Ocağı]]\n[[zh:采石场]]"
    }
